title: Star Network - Social DeFi

creator: Big Leap Limited
descriptionHtml:
Referral Code: starexplorer

Star Network, your all-in-one Social DeFi app for growing, holding and using your Star balance and communicating with your social network. We have now entered KYC phase and users can now initiate P2P transfer.

Star Network features a comprehensive functions including:
1. In-app instant messenger with photo-sharing functions
2. Drawing Libra token to unlock your KYC slot & Realized Balance
3. KYC by trusted 3rd party to enhance data privacy and security
4. Active wallet for growing your Star Balance and initiate Peer-to-Peer (P2P) transactions

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- introduced Convertible Balance
- added new function of drawing LIBRA, the unlocking token, every 12 hours.
- users who got a LIBRA can submit personal information for KYC to 3rd-party compliance company
- activated wallet status for every users (both KYC-ed and non-KYC-ed). User can do P2P transfer now when you have Realized Balance in your wallet.

descriptionHtml:
Star Network is an all-inclusive app for you to grow, hold and transfer your Star balance. In addition to decentralized finance, the app also features mobile game and social networking elements for you to earn, play and social with Star Network to become GameFi!

Core Functions of Star Network include:
1. Grow, hold and stake your Star balance
2. KYC via trusted 3rd-party
3. P2P transfer to all users of Star Network
4. Instant messenger with photo-sharing functions
5. Mobile games tournament for GameFi
